Task 2:
Create a website with this design: https://assets.digitalocean.com/articles/how-to-build-a-website-with-html/html-demo-site.gif

Exchange the content by your own text. The title should be “[YOUR NAME] the Shark” and write your own short introduction text.

In the tips you have a bunch of tutorials that can guide you in this task.

Send a PR targeting a branch with your name (if it doesn’t exist, please ask me to create) at https://github.com/flaviostutz/onboarding-web-students and a screenshot of the page.

Tips:
  - https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorial_series/how-to-build-a-website-with-html
  - https://www.tutorialrepublic.com/html-examples.php